          <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">Window Installation Expert • FENSA Knowledge Specialist • Building Regulations Advisor</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <!-- Profile Card -->
          <div class="lg:col-span-1">
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-green-50 to-green-100 p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm">
              <div class="text-center mb-6">
                <img 
                  src="/images/oliver-greene-profilepic_compressed_compressed.webp" 
                  alt="Oliver Greene - Professional headshot"
                  class="w-32 h-32 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 shadow-lg"
                />
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800">Oliver Greene</h3>
                <p class="text-green-600 font-medium">Industry Expert & Consultant</p>
              </div>
              
              <!-- Credentials -->
              <div class="space-y-3">
                <div class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">FENSA Knowledge Specialist</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Building Regulations Advisor</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">38 Years Industry Experience</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Conservation Area Specialist</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Experience Story -->
          <div class="lg:col-span-2">
            <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
              <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                Oliver began his career in 1986 as an apprentice installer, working on everything from heritage timber sash restorations to advanced aluminium glazing systems. Over nearly four decades, he built deep expertise in:
              </p>
              
              <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-8">
                <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2 flex items-center">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-4m-5 0H9m0 0H5m0 0h2M7 7h10M7 11h10M7 15h10"></path>
                    </svg>
                    UK Building Regulations
                  </h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Part L energy efficiency, Part F ventilation, and compliance requirements</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2 flex items-center">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-4m-5 0H9m0 0H5m0 0h2M7 7h10M7 11h10M7 15h10"></path>
                    </svg>
                    Conservation Area Rules
                  </h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Listed building consent, heritage requirements, and planning permissions</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2 flex items-center">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
                    </svg>
                    Energy-Efficient Upgrades
                  </h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Advanced glazing, thermal performance, and sustainable solutions</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2 flex items-center">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                    </svg>
                    Installer Vetting
                  </h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Quality assessment, certification verification, and best practice standards</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <blockquote class="border-l-4 border-green-500 pl-6 italic text-xl text-gray-700 mb-6">
                "I started this platform to cut through the confusion. Most people just want straight answers and a trustworthy recommendation. That's what I offer."
              </blockquote>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Trust Indicators -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">Why Homeowners Trust Us</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Built on decades of real-world experience and a commitment to honest, pressure-free advice
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- Trust Factor 1 -->
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z"></path>
